Popular Brands

























Mattresses on sale in our catalog run the gamut from plush to firm and twin to king. Find every style and size, from a Tempur-Pedic to an adjustable bed base. Made by top mattress brands such as Stearns & Foster and Sealy, our mattresses are just what you need for a better night’s rest.
Adjustable bed bases make it possible to tailor your bed’s position to your body, improving comfort and relaxation with a custom fit. Enjoy the ultimate sleeping experience with our selection of adjustable bedding foundations!
Bed frames and bedding accessories complete your new bed so that you can start enjoying a better sleep experience right away. Shop our selection of bed frames and accessories to find pillows and frames that cater to your needs.
Learn more about the best mattress for you in our Mattress Buying Guide — because when you’re wondering where to buy the mattress you want, we’re here to help at Conn’s HomePlus. We not only offer a wide selection of king and queen mattresses, adjustable bed bases, bed frames and bedding accessories, but we also provide financing to help you get what you need. Even if you’ve been turned down elsewhere, you may qualify for our financing program. Learn more about our mattress financing and apply for your YES MONEY® credit today!
 



