Refrigerators







Say “YES” to a Kitchen Upgrade
 If there’s one thing that makes a kitchen look like a brand new room, it's a new energy-efficient refrigerator from Conn’s HomePlus.





            The right refrigerator can make all the difference in the style and usability of a kitchen. If you’re looking to upgrade your refrigerator to one with all of today’s modern features, Conn’s HomePlus has you covered. We have a variety of styles and features available – side-by-side units, French doors, super capacity – from top brands like Samsung, LG, Whirlpool and more.  Conn’s HomePlus is your resource for finding the best refrigerator to complete your kitchen. We also offer a fine selection of deep-freeze freezers and mini fridges. Whether you’re interested in a counter-depth refrigerator, side-by-side refrigerator, French door refrigerator or something else, we’ve got what you’re looking for. Explore our selection! Learn more about our latest refrigerator financing deals. 

 



