Furniture & Mattresses







Find Furniture for Every Room
 Whether you're looking to fill your office, apartment, or home with new furniture, Conn's HomePlus has a great selection and low prices on all types of furniture and mattresses.






NO INTEREST UNTIL 2020**
on all furniture & mattress purchases $1999 and up
with your Conn's Credit Card between 7/16/17 & 7/22/17.
Equal monthly payments required for 30 mos.








FREE HDTV OR FREE NEXT DAY DELIVERY
on all furniture & mattress purchases $1999 and up.


Shop Now



 


            At Conn’s HomePlus, you can choose from a wide variety of quality furniture, including stylish sofas and sectionals, dining tables, bedroom sets and more. Tuck yourself in for a good night’s sleep with an affordable new mattress and bedding set. We offer all the latest developments in sleep technology, from individually wrapped coils to memory foam. Make your house a home with quality furniture and name brand mattresses from Conn’s HomePlus!        




