^ Segal, David. "How to Pierce a Deafening Silence? Maybe an Army Can Help." The New York Times. July 3, 2014. Retrieved on July 19, 2014.
^ Segal, David. "Many Are Knocking, but the Door Stays Closed." The New York Times. July 19, 2014. Retrieved on July 19, 2014.


